Now we just have to get you to a game. 

PS IT was the Snooper bowl and when the game was over and we finally came to the presser we were in a team Moms tiny car all muddy because it was ice storm if you recall!  Always about the kids is right 👊🏽

@deionsanders @gojsutigersfb @smacentertainment @shedeursanders @snoopdogg @snoopleague

#Repost @deionsanders with @make_repost
・・・
I’m doing what god called me to do. I’ve had my time with the NFL, there’s a common misconception that it’s been about me when it never has been. Everything I do has been for @mommaconnie21 & the kids. I’m dedicated to doing everything I can for them to achieve the goals they tell me they want to achieve. To create change you have to do things different and I am here to create change. This happened in 2011 and PrimeTime has kept on Ticking baby. @richeisen @snoopdogg @richeisenshow @smacentertainment @conschwartz

Repost from @conschwartz
•
Now we just have to get you to a game. 

PS IT was the Snooper bowl and when the game was over and we finally came to the presser we were in a team Moms tiny car all muddy because it was ice storm if you recall!  Always about the kids is right 👊🏽

@deionsanders @gojsutigersfb @smacentertainment @shedeursanders @snoopdogg @snoopleague

#Repost @deionsanders with @make_repost
・・・
I’m doing what god called me to do. I’ve had my time with the NFL, there’s a common misconception that it’s been about me when it never has been. Everything I do has been for @mommaconnie21 & the kids. I’m dedicated to doing everything I can for them to achieve the goals they tell me they want to achieve. To create change you have to do things different and I am here to create change. This happened in 2011 and PrimeTime has kept on Ticking baby. @richeisen @snoopdogg @richeisenshow @smacentertainment @conschwartz
